"""
SCHEDULE IIRegulation 6(6)(c) HOUSING COSTS

Persons residing with the claimant

14.

(2)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

In the case of a non-dependant aged 18 or over to whom sub-paragraph (1)(a) applies because he is in remunerative work, where the claimant satisfies the Secretary of State that the non-dependant’s gross weekly income is—

(d)

not less than £334.00 but less than £445.00, the deduction to be made under this paragraph shall be £99.65;
"""

housing_costs_non_dependant_age_threshold_for_paragraph_14_2_d:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Integer
    from 2025-03-21:
        18

housing_costs_non_dependant_gross_weekly_income_lower_threshold_for_paragraph_14_2_d:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Money
    from 2025-03-21:
        334.00

housing_costs_non_dependant_gross_weekly_income_upper_threshold_for_paragraph_14_2_d:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Money
    from 2025-03-21:
        445.00

housing_costs_non_dependant_deduction_amount_for_paragraph_14_2_d:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Money
    from 2025-03-21:
        99.65

housing_costs_non_dependant_is_aged_18_or_over_for_paragraph_14_2_d:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        person.age >= housing_costs_non_dependant_age_threshold_for_paragraph_14_2_d

housing_costs_subparagraph_1_a_applies_because_non_dependant_is_in_remunerative_work:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Boolean

housing_costs_non_dependant_gross_weekly_income:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Money

housing_costs_non_dependant_deduction_paragraph_14_2_d:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Money
    from 2025-03-21:
        if housing_costs_non_dependant_is_aged_18_or_over_for_paragraph_14_2_d and housing_costs_subparagraph_1_a_applies_because_non_dependant_is_in_remunerative_work and housing_costs_non_dependant_gross_weekly_income >= housing_costs_non_dependant_gross_weekly_income_lower_threshold_for_paragraph_14_2_d and housing_costs_non_dependant_gross_weekly_income < housing_costs_non_dependant_gross_weekly_income_upper_threshold_for_paragraph_14_2_d: housing_costs_non_dependant_deduction_amount_for_paragraph_14_2_d else: 0
